Name: Verify that the bike can turn its direction during driving
Description: Verify that the driver can easily turn the bike left/right while moving
Preconditions: User has the bike switched on.
Step by step actions to follow:
1.	Get on the bike and accelerate the speed.
2.	Turn the steering wheel left to check if the direction is correctly changed
3.	Turn the steering wheel right to check if the direction is correctly changed
Expected outcome: The bike changes directions without any problems.
